unite-sorce for BEAR (inspired by unite-rails)

Usage:
  Unite bear/App
    : BEAR_HOME/App/

  Unite bear/htdocs
    : BEAR_HOME/htdocs/

  Unite bear/libs
    : BEAR_HOME/libs/

  Unite bear/Form
    : BEAR_HOME/App/Form

  Unite bear/Page
    : BEAR_HOME/App/Page/

  Unite bear/Ro
    : BEAR_HOME/App/Ro/

  Unite bear/views
    : BEAR_HOME/App/views/
